    "name": "Mind Her Manor",
    "steam_appid": 3129920,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/a0095bb2daf5a7f2d07043b3e408b605.poster.avif?t=1767381192\" width=510 height=133 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/a0095bb2daf5a7f2d07043b3e408b605.webm?t=1767381192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mind Her Manor is an action-adventure game with management elements. Young Henrietta finds herself as the newest prisoner to be taken into the manor of Fay Shadowrend, the Matriarch of Witches. Fate seems to smile upon her as she is released from her cold cell, selected to do Fay's bidding. Free to wander the manor, Henrietta must find a way to escape Fay's clutches as she keeps her satisfied.  Henrietta will encounter numerous characters, ferocious enemies, and perplexing puzzles as she works for her life! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/1a69301992e5d5d22c420af0580046f5.poster.avif?t=1767381192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/1a69301992e5d5d22c420af0580046f5.webm?t=1767381192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/1a69301992e5d5d22c420af0580046f5.mp4?t=1767381192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mind Her Manor is the first project of Mindbridge Games, consisting mainly of two developers, and is made on GameMaker. It features anthropomorphic animals as its characters and a high fantasy medieval setting. Its gameplay is inspired by Zelda, Dead Rising, Secret of Mana, and Resident Evil.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/fbb31a17b3c05fd6b61c99ccc8333f51.poster.avif?t=1767381192\" width=510 height=133 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/fbb31a17b3c05fd6b61c99ccc8333f51.webm?t=1767381192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A top-down perspective with 8-directional movement, both keyboard/mouse and controller support! (analog movement available on controllers)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a lavish medieval manor as you accomplish Fay's tasks. Manage your time wisely!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plentiful randomization including random loot and periodic enemy spawns.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A cast of interesting characters with their own quests!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A handful of endings depending on who you support.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Copious puzzles to help ease your journey or offer the keys to freedom!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A set of four weapons to help defend against the monsters of the manor. Build your charge bar and release powerful charge attacks!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A terrifying creature of the night that persists across rooms...</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brew an array of potent potions from monster parts and acquire temporary buffs of all kinds!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cutscenes featuring full body pictures of speaking characters!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A bevy of curious items to help you in your quest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maintain your weapons and other gear.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An original soundtrack, most tracks composed by Anna Maria Olsson.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/4b5eda2c38009c6aaea0b379805a95d2.poster.avif?t=1767381192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/4b5eda2c38009c6aaea0b379805a95d2.webm?t=1767381192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/4b5eda2c38009c6aaea0b379805a95d2.mp4?t=1767381192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/6a1bc4e762e2cca3839ed2a4b6374d3c.poster.avif?t=1767381192\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/6a1bc4e762e2cca3839ed2a4b6374d3c.webm?t=1767381192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/6a1bc4e762e2cca3839ed2a4b6374d3c.mp4?t=1767381192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/743cf162dff42e43f40753a545abeeeb.poster.avif?t=1767381192\" width=510 height=133 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3129920/extras/743cf162dff42e43f40753a545abeeeb.webm?t=1767381192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fidchell - Project Lead, Artist, Programmer, Writer, Composer, Character Designer, Sound Artist</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gibmaker/Sejuay - Lead Programmer</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flame Kerandia &amp; Starskimmer - Assisting Programmers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anna Maria Olsson - Composer</p>",
